LibPKU Browser Extension enhances experience of various pku.edu.cn websites including:
- Displays a red logo when visiting official pku.edu.cn websites to help you distinguish fake websites;
- Allow you to batch download course videos at course.pku.edu.cn;
- Allow you to get download link of shared file at disk.pku.edu.cn;
And more functionalities are developing.
